// Login Bonus slot indices that grant a Dawn Ticket (0-indexed within the 7-slot week)
// Odd ISO week: slots 1, 4, 6 (day 2, 5, 7); Even: slots 0, 2, 5 (day 1, 3, 6)
// Slot 3 is always reserved for the Moonrise/Starlight/Solstice gacha ticket.
